'''Rebel survey teams''' were tasked by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]] with surveying planets to see if they were suitable for base locations. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] led one such team to [[Arbra/Legends|Arbra]] after the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]]. The teams dressed in white uniforms and commonly employed [[air bike]]s and [[Plastent/Legends|plastents]].

